title: Print, "The Last Days of Harvest, from Harper's Weekly, December 6, 1873, p. 1092.", December 6, 1873
medium: Wood engraving in black ink on newsprint paper.
description: Horizontal scene showing, in the foreground, two small boys seated and husking corn with an open wagon filled with pumpkins in the background.
